data.description: Fabulous 3 bedroom/3.5 bathroom home in Wildwood! Home has spacious rooms throughout, including kitchen, living room, family room, dining room and a large deck in the back for indoor and outdoor entertainment. There is also a fenced backyard, a 3 car heated garage, and an incredible primary bedroom suite with tons of closet space, a whirlpool tub, and a deck to step outside and enjoy the view. All appliances stay and there is a 1 Year TMI Home Warranty as well. Come and see!
